Method Detail

createFieldEditors

protected void createFieldEditors()
Depending on the preference default class AbstractWorkspacePreference.getDefaultClazz() a field editor is created. The label of a preference is translated by Messages.getString(String, Object...) with message key "<PreferenceSimpleClassName>.<PrefenceName>.PreferencePageLabel".

Specified by:
createFieldEditors in class org.eclipse.jface.preference.FieldEditorPreferencePage

init

public void init(org.eclipse.ui.IWorkbench _iworkbench)
Initialize the preference page by defining the description and the workspace preference store of the plug-in for this preference page. The description is translated by calling method Messages.getString(String, Object...) with message key "<PreferenceSimpleClassName>.PreferencePageDescription".
